00:27:08,801 --> 00:27:11,151
And this building.

513
00:27:13,893 --> 00:27:15,503
And you.

514
00:27:17,853 --> 00:27:19,638
No complaints, Maggie.

515
00:27:22,771 --> 00:27:24,033
Excuse me.

516
00:27:28,951 --> 00:27:30,910
