517
00:27:39,135 --> 00:27:41,094
[elevator bell dings]

518
00:27:58,851 --> 00:28:01,157
♪ ♪

519
00:28:07,468 --> 00:28:09,470
Just be yourself.

520
00:28:09,513 --> 00:28:11,298
Relaxed.

521
00:28:11,341 --> 00:28:12,995
- But don't try to be funny.
- [laughs]

522
00:28:13,039 --> 00:28:14,431
You're not very funny.

523
00:28:14,475 --> 00:28:16,085
- What is...
