524
00:28:16,129 --> 00:28:17,739
What is this about?
[chuckles]

525
00:28:17,783 --> 00:28:20,611
Just... be cool.

526
00:28:20,655 --> 00:28:24,093
But not I.A. cool,
not frosty cool.

527
00:28:24,137 --> 00:28:27,706
Just be your lovely self.

528
00:28:27,749 --> 00:28:29,708
GUZMIN: Hello, hello,
hello, hello, hello.

529
00:28:29,751 --> 00:28:31,057
Hi.

530
00:28:31,100 --> 00:28:32,841
- Look at you.
- [laughs]

531
00:28:32,885 --> 00:28:34,843
- I can't believe it.
- It's so good to see you.

532
00:28:34,887 --> 00:28:36,497
[faintly]:
So good to see you.

533
00:28:42,808 --> 00:28:44,592
I want you to meet someone.

534
00:28:44,635 --> 00:28:46,637
GUZMIN:
Ah.

535
00:28:50,032 --> 00:28:51,425
[chuckles]

536
00:28:52,469 --> 00:28:54,123
Hey, man.

537
00:28:54,167 --> 00:28:57,387
♪ ♪

538
00:28:58,954 --> 00:29:00,739
Oh, so, uh...
[chuckles]

539
00:29:00,782 --> 00:29:03,567
This is Daniel. This is Guzmin.

540
00:29:03,611 --> 00:29:05,004
My old friend.

541
00:29:05,047 --> 00:29:06,527
Pleased to meet you, uh...

542
00:29:06,570 --> 00:29:09,530
I hear I have to pass
some sort of test?

543
00:29:09,573 --> 00:29:11,880
- You passed it.
- Cool.

544
00:29:11,924 --> 00:29:14,187
- What did I do?
- Nothing.

545
00:29:14,230 --> 00:29:17,320
I saw it in her eyes,
the moment I saw her.

546
00:29:18,800 --> 00:29:20,802
Guzmin.

547
00:29:20,846 --> 00:29:24,588
I was never looking
at the man, Maggie.

548
00:29:24,632 --> 00:29:26,939
I was looking at your eyes.

549
00:29:30,507 --> 00:29:33,554
- Well, that was easy. [chuckles]
- Don't blow it.

550
00:29:33,597 --> 00:29:35,948
Hello, little monkey. Come here.

551
00:29:35,991 --> 00:29:38,559
- [giggling]
- [chuckles] Look at you.

552
00:29:38,602 --> 00:29:41,649
Look at you, look at you,
my little monkey.

553
00:29:41,692 --> 00:29:43,782
Look at you.

554
00:29:43,825 --> 00:29:46,828
I can't believe she's eight.
I can't believe she's here.

555
00:29:46,872 --> 00:29:48,438
So how was
your airplane flight? Good?

556
00:29:48,482 --> 00:29:50,049
DANIEL:
Yeah, it was, uh...

557
00:29:50,092 --> 00:29:52,051
[Guzmin and Daniel
talking quietly]

558
00:29:55,054 --> 00:29:57,012
What do you most
want to do today?

