00:30:03,802 --> 00:30:08,241
♪ The girl who fell to Earth ♪

560
00:30:08,284 --> 00:30:11,244
♪ Ooh ♪

561
00:30:12,419 --> 00:30:16,423
♪ Ooh ♪

562
00:30:20,427 --> 00:30:25,911
