563
00:30:25,954 --> 00:30:28,565
♪ Ooh ♪

564
00:30:30,002 --> 00:30:34,615
♪ Ooh, ah ♪

565
00:30:37,618 --> 00:30:41,927
♪ First you cry
and then you laugh ♪

566
00:30:41,970 --> 00:30:45,844
♪ You're like a circle,
cut in half ♪

